high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white table to the left of the television, and stand in front of the three credit cards.
Pick up the credit card that's closest to the television.
Turn and face the yellow chair with the purple cushion on it.
Place the credit card in front of the purple cushion.
Turn right and face the white table with the sculpture on it.
Pick up the credit card that's closest to the sculpture.
Turn around to face the yellow chair with the first credit card on it.
Put the second credit card on the chair to the right of the purple cushion.
anns.task_desc: To place two credit cards on the yellow chair.

high_descs: Turn around and go forward, then hang a right and go to the white table that is right of the yellow chair.
Pick up the blue credit card that is the farthest to the right.
Turn around and go to the yellow chair on the right.
Put the credit card on the chair in front of the purple pillow.
Turn to the right and go to the white table.
Pick up the credit card that is farthest to the left.
Turn around and go to the yellow chair on the right.
Put the credit card on the chair to the left of the purple pillow.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on a chair.

high_descs: Move to the end table to the left of the TV
Pick up a card from the end table
Move to the arm chair to the left
Place the card on the chair
Move to the end table to the left of the TV
Pick up a card from the end table
Move to the arm chair to the left
Place the card on the chair
anns.task_desc: Put two cards on the arm chair to the left of the TV.
